---
title: Cheesy Pumpkin & Veggie Bake with Crunchy Pangrattato & Pear Salad
description: Everyone loves a bubbling bake fresh out of the oven. This one includes wholesome roasted veggies, a rich, homemade tomato
sauce and a crunchy pangrattato. Finish it off with a sprinkling of two types of cheese to guarantee a decadence reserved for someone special such as yourself!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
